  "texts": [
    "All participants signed an informed consent for the SS protocol.",
    "Acquisition and preprocessing of speech dataThe SS protocol was carried out using the acceX ible platform on a tablet.",
    "The assessments were conducted in Spanish within a calm and controlled environment.",
    "Initially, the participants were presented The Cookie Theft Picture and were instructed to provide a comprehensive description of the image [44].",
    "Subsequently, they were given one minute to name as many different animals as possible."
  ]
}